{"tid":753845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶][支那]冷血官僚 不救人 只顧搶通車","createTime":"2018-07-24T02:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T02:58:15.000Z","uid":144924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64c05a265a652ef2ac6e773d711c73e6deabc2dc","tid":753845,"uid":144924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"2011年的今天，北京南站開往福州站的D301次列車與杭州站開往福州南站的D3115次列車追尾相撞，40人死亡，172人受傷。有媒體稱，當局在次日早上開始迫不及待清理現場，用鏟車將墜落車廂碎片碾壓後挖坑就地掩埋。亦有新聞稱這是由於四節墜地車廂因體積太大，無法運出現場。此舉引發民眾激烈反應，認為車廂中可能還有倖存人員、遇難者遺體及遺物，並認為此舉是為「毀屍滅跡」，試圖掩蓋事件真相，毀滅問責證據。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/105155_6108e0d7f73ff15b65f69d2bdb1a830c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F105155_6108e0d7f73ff15b65f69d2bdb1a830c.png&h=9e687021&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/105156_5dc739f7a98a1f9c09a37704c4ed2bb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F105156_5dc739f7a98a1f9c09a37704c4ed2bb2.png&h=33fd5fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/105434_60d2c890017f009f3842ef7bcadd8fbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F105434_60d2c890017f009f3842ef7bcadd8fbe.png&h=4a123cc3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}